         <abstract id="aspace_c44de802bb5452e18eb35bad8dd2b51e">The Associate Board of the Women's Christian College, Madras, was the American governing body of the College, which was founded in 1915 in Madras, India, as a joint venture of several British and American mission boards.</abstract>
